name: Las Vegas Air Conditioning and AC Repair
description:
Las Vegas Air Conditioning and AC Repair provides top-notch heating, ventilation and air conditioning (HVAC). As well as great customer care, support, and prices that are fair and competitive


Commercial and Residential Air Conditioner (AC) Repair

    * All makes and models of heating, air conditioning, commercial refrigeration systems       and ice machines.
    * Computer and Telephone room air conditioning systems repair.
    * Make recommendations for proper system operation.
    * Explain repair, options and price to inform the customer of the benefits of long term       and short term repairs.
    * Duct repair and modification (leaking and deteriorating).
    * Authorized warranty repair center for most major brands.
    * Reclaim and recycle refrigerants.
    * System Cleaning.
